```tsx
function cva(base?: ClassValue, config?: Config): (props?) => string
```
Creates variant-based className functions from `class-variance-authority`. Used to define reusable component variants.

```tsx
const buttonVariants = cva("inline-flex items-center", {
  variants: {
    variant: { default: "bg-primary", outline: "border" },
    size: { default: "h-10 px-4", sm: "h-9 px-3" },
  },
  defaultVariants: { variant: "default", size: "default" },
});
```

